  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Articles create landmark regions that screen readers can navigate to</li>
      <li>Always include a heading (h1-h6) to label the article content</li>
      <li>Use <code>&lt;header&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> within articles for structured metadata</li>
      <li>Include <code>&lt;time&gt;</code> elements with <code>datetime</code> attributes for publication dates</li>
      <li>Nested articles maintain proper heading hierarchy (avoid skipping levels)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

